text: Hussein Sherif is an Egyptian taekwondo practitioner. Sherif won the bronze medal in the men's finweight (under 54 kg) division at the 2013 World Taekwondo Championships in Puebla. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Egyptian male taekwondo practitioners Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists
